Description: Round-topped limestone stela with high relief detail divided into three registers: 1 - Winged sun-disc with pendent uraei; jackals below. 2 - Scene of the deceased being led by Anubis before the enthroned figure of Osiris. 3 - Two lines of Demotic text(very faint). Traces of painted detail.
Curator's comments: No Demotic present, according to Damien Agut (2006)
